By the name of the most high

In this year l experienced many of problems such as the problem with my maternal aunt; or about the stress of school or gym.Some times I think that I am the most stupid person in the world and I don’t have anybody to support me in the problems.in my idea everybody can make their future by themselves I mean our behavior and people might like it or hate us. 

Today I discuss a lot and I don’t feel relax and I think I am the worst person in the world and this is right because its true and I discuss with my Razyeh aunt for many difference between our ideas and I tried a lot to tell her to forgive me but l cant .she always order me l mean everybody and I have problem with ordering or nagging. She will not stop ordering and I don’t want to say this that really I don’t like her. Not her personality I don’t like her behaviors .They aren’t so politely.
